meaningMnemonic: The <kanji>most</kanji> <kanji>tall</kanji> isn't literally the most tall. When you think of something high above the rest, you think of something that is <vocabulary>the best</vocabulary>.
readingMnemonic: This is a jukugo word, which usually means on'yomi readings from the kanji. If you know the readings of your kanji you'll know how to read this as well.
